levels of access

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:27.230
students from
different backgrounds

00:03:27.230 --> 00:03:29.930
are able to attain as they
seek college admission.

00:03:29.930 --> 00:03:32.780
So thinking about these
tests as a key lever--

00:03:32.780 --> 00:03:35.180
