00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:55.460
environments.

00:05:55.460 --> 00:05:58.260
And the benefit to kind of
getting at skills in that way

00:05:58.260 --> 00:06:00.460
is you allow high
schools to maybe,

00:06:00.460 --> 00:06:02.300
if they're based
