00:06:02.300 --> 00:06:03.980
on teaching subject
matter that's

00:06:03.980 --> 00:06:06.590
very different than high schools
that are based in Pasadena

00:06:06.590 --> 00:06:07.880
or based in Boston.

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:09.950
So you're able to
move away from just,

00:06:09.950 --> 00:06:13.040
can you plow through
180 days of a textbook?

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:14.960
And towards project
based learning,

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:17.270
or application based learning,
or flipped classrooms.

00:06:17.270 --> 00:06:19.250
There's a whole variety
of different solutions

00:06:19.250 --> 00:06:21.480
that kind of try and
inculcate deeper skills,

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:24.320
as opposed to more content,
